{"tid":1797525,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"我開左一個教畫動漫人物既班","createTime":"2019-12-25T13:34:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T02:27:04.000Z","uid":122247,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fccae9b735b4f8c19f736aa3e0c6148f003b6a0b","tid":1797525,"uid":122247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T13:34:41.000Z","msg":"利申，這是廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n是咁的，我開左一個教畫人物既畫班<br />\n專門係for想學畫日系動漫風既朋友<br />\n課程由最基本既十字線畫頭到進階少少既人物比例都會教<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6XgLAcp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6XgLAcp.jpg&h=6d7d1106&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/34Pxfcq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F34Pxfcq.jpg&h=e4bee3ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iW7635U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiW7635U.jpg&h=5906ea48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n至於我到底有咩資格開班教人呢？<br />\n其實呢個班只係for入門或者一D本身有畫開畫既朋友<br />\n所以唔會好深入<br />\n而作為一個曾於香港、美國及其他國家連載過漫畫既人<br />\n我絕對有信心教到一D你自學時要花好多時間先學到既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有咩問題都可以係到問我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n課程資料:<br />\n<br />\n活動：漫畫 &mdash; 人物課程<br />\n內容：以教授手繪動漫人物為課程主軸，希望學生在課堂完成後能繪畫出滿意的漫畫角色，以培養學生繪畫的興趣。<br />\n日期：1月5日、1月12日、1月19日、2月2日<br />\n地點：青年夢工場（屯門井財街政府服務大樓四樓）<br />\n時間：15:00-17:00<br />\n名額：8 人（二人同行85折；另外兩位免費名額給予全額／半額學生資助或來自綜援家庭的學生）<br />\n導師：Costo（漫畫導師）<br />\n費用：四堂$1200、$800（學生優惠）<br />\n報名及繳費：<a href=\"https://forms.gle/k44ddnxttY1fNgeEA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2Fk44ddnxttY1fNgeEA&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFIDkkQuUBcdRTUhzZaMUkok%3D&h=15c8edec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/k44ddnxttY1fNgeEA</a><br />\n導師作品：<a href=\"https://tapas.io/episode/1273037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftapas.io%2Fepisode%2F1273037&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFIDkkQuUBcdRTUhzZaMUkok%3D&h=3d31f509\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tapas.io/episode/1273037</a><br />\n<br />\n第一課：頭部<br />\n教授繪畫人物五官、髮型以及臉型的概念，指導繪畫男女老幼時的分別。並教授如何繪畫不同表情。<br />\n<br />\n第二課：身體比例 (一）<br />\n教授繪畫人物上身，包括胸部、肩頸以及手部等的基本技巧，並指導特別需要注意的細節。<br />\n<br />\n第三堂：身體比例 (二）<br />\n教授繪畫人物全身，並指導男女老幼角色之間的比例分別，再教授如何以頭身比方式作畫。<br />\n<br />\n第四堂：完整人物<br />\n教授繪畫衣物的基本技巧，並指導如何畫出富動感或魅力的角色 (不包括上色）。"},{"pid":"d7ab3c71c6c8e481aacd816dfbe2a08c660c9e93","tid":1797525,"uid":201414,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T13:37:39.000Z","msg":"乜呢家連登變左廣告雜誌咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f26335a0db157b68220ef15cd46ba610008003a0","tid":1797525,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T13:38:21.000Z","msg":"1200蚊淨係教畫人物係咪貴左d<br />\n得罪講句睇你個作品你呢個價起碼要教埋點畫背景同特效先夠皮"},{"pid":"252d6cfd52f8964a317bf29775d51df2e267239f","tid":1797525,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T14:31:43.000Z","msg":"教唔教畫H COMIC"},{"pid":"370525e7112e12202a7b09f7b8afe633b7d5a241","tid":1797525,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T14:58:12.000Z","msg":"人物比例代表作：足球小將"},{"pid":"a7edfbc35d09c7be6a5eeee9b75c590ce4328c2e","tid":1797525,"uid":82068,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T15:30:18.000Z","msg":"畫幾張h漫黎睇下先"},{"pid":"8250ca759d8bdadf2ed03feb8bd02bba11ba9f49","tid":1797525,"uid":87428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T17:02:38.000Z","msg":"雖然覺得唔夠日本風<br />\n似外國啲超仿日漫畫<br />\n<br />\n鼓勵人去學 可能你都係未來黃玉郎<br />\n係香港漫畫家"},{"pid":"b49dd9f634eae84601ae5aec01be2a3d6da58cfe","tid":1797525,"uid":303359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T17:11:10.000Z","msg":"會唔會教畫h漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3383199c21cad6597830331abb7904c58814d83c","tid":1797525,"uid":31323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T02:27:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/89/62/q5iRpqCWlqaYrKQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F89%2F62%2Fq5iRpqCWlqaYrKQ.jpg&h=d8d10995&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}